title: Tokyo Joes
typeOfFood: Japanese, Fast food, Take-out, Asian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Veg choices include edamame, veggie gyoza (dumpling), and the Boulder veggie bowl. Many sauces and dressings are vegan like the teriyaki, yakatori and peanut sauce, sesame and miso dressing. For dessert a krispie bar. Also a location at 100 W. Troutman Parkway, Fort Collins.
